s insufficient, which can impact bone health, immune function, and potentially increase cardiovascular risk. Consider supplementation or increasing sun exposure.\n\nOverall, your lipid profile and cholesterol ratios are the most concerning areas, indicating an increased risk for heart disease and stroke. Addressing these through dietary changes, exercise, and potentially medication is crucial. Regular monitoring and follow-up with your healthcare provider are recommended.','\n',char(10)),'2025-04-03 10:47:28.625725','fa9800f4-3cf6-402b-aa14-2adfbdac91d4');
